description:
Math Pro is a refreshing way to improve your mathematical skills. 

It will help you:
 
- In improving mental arithmetic
- speed up your ability to perform calculations quickly
- improve in problems solving
- have fun competing with yourself and your friends 

Test settings are highly configurable:

- Difficulty levels (Easy, Medium, Hard and Expert)
- Number of questions in test
- Total time required for test


This app includes following categories:

- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication 
- Division 
- Mixed

Each category has 3 chapters, and we can practice them multiple times, because the questions are randomly generated, this way you will have indefinite learning.

All the completed test results are archived for tracking your performance.


Note: In case of issues, please contact me by e-mail before leaving a negative review.
